name: DASHPrice
0:
”Alexa, ask DASH Price what the current price of DASH is.”
”Alexa, ask DASH Price to get the current price of DASH.”
”Alexa, ask DASH Price how much DASH is.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dash price
des: DASH Price allows you to quickly figure out what the market price of DASH is in US dollars. Simply ask Alexa how much DASH is and get an instant answer. Perfect for figuring out when the right times are for buying and selling and just keeping up with price movements throughout the day.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
